```class Solution {
    public int[] earliestAndLatest(int n, int firstPlayer, int secondPlayer) {
        int earliest = Math.max(1, Math.abs(firstPlayer - secondPlayer) + 1);
        int latest = Math.min(n, n - Math.abs(firstPlayer - secondPlayer) + 1);
        return new int[]{earliest, latest};
    }
}```
